and I gave him to me master.

260
00:25:38.440 --> 00:25:41.716
And I'll make any man
or thing else vanish I like.

261
00:25:41.800 --> 00:25:43.518
- No.
- Aye.

262
00:25:43.600 --> 00:25:45.670
