363
00:33:43.800 --> 00:33:46.633
<font color="#808080">WILLIAM:</font> Go to.

364
00:33:47.200 --> 00:33:50.510
<font color="#808080">KATHERINE:</font>
God save us, Caleb is well.

365
00:33:50.600 --> 00:33:52.511
<font color="#808080">WILLIAM:</font> We must keep him still.
